{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":491,"text":"Adam Ockelford: I promise there won't be too much"},{"time":1836,"text":"of me talking, and a lot of Derek playing,"},{"time":4248,"text":"but I thought it would just be nice to recap"},{"time":6692,"text":"on how Derek got to where he is today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10628,"text":"It's amazing now, because he's so much bigger than me,"},{"time":13119,"text":"but when Derek was born,"},{"time":14737,"text":"he could have fitted on the palm of your hand."},{"time":17376,"text":"He was born three and a half months premature,"},{"time":20340,"text":"and really it was a fantastic fight for him to survive."},{"time":25556,"text":"He had to have a lot of oxygen,"},{"time":26776,"text":"and that affected your eyes, Derek,"},{"time":28776,"text":"and also the way you understand language"},{"time":30604,"text":"and the way you understand the world."},{"time":33575,"text":"But that was the end of the bad news,"},{"time":35657,"text":"because when Derek came home from the hospital,"},{"time":38648,"text":"his family decided to employ the redoubtable nanny"},{"time":41830,"text":"who was going to look after you, Derek,"},{"time":44201,"text":"really for the rest of your childhood."},{"time":46849,"text":"And Nanny's great insight, really,"},{"time":49425,"text":"was to think, here's a child who can't see."},{"time":52110,"text":"Music must be the thing for Derek."},{"time":55031,"text":"And sure enough, she sang, or as Derek called it, warbled,"},{"time":59298,"text":"to him for his first few years of life."},{"time":62843,"text":"And I think it was that excitement with hearing her voice"},{"time":66894,"text":"hour after hour every day that made him think"},{"time":69878,"text":"maybe, you know, in his brain something was stirring,"},{"time":72896,"text":"some sort of musical gift."},{"time":75905,"text":"Here's a little picture of Derek going up now,"},{"time":78178,"text":"when you were with your nanny."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81852,"text":"Now Nanny's great other insight was to think,"},{"time":85371,"text":"perhaps we should get Derek something to play,"},{"time":88706,"text":"and sure enough, she dragged this little keyboard"},{"time":92342,"text":"out of the loft, never thinking really"},{"time":94938,"text":"that anything much would come of it."},{"time":97281,"text":"But Derek, your tiny hand must have gone out to that thing"},{"time":100269,"text":"and actually bashed it,"},{"time":101890,"text":"bashed it so hard they thought it was going to break."},{"time":104679,"text":"But out of all the bashing, after a few months,"},{"time":108671,"text":"emerged the most fantastic music,"},{"time":111840,"text":"and I think there was just a miracle moment, really, Derek,"},{"time":115206,"text":"when you realized that all the sounds you hear in the world"},{"time":119721,"text":"out there is something that you can copy on the keyboard."},{"time":123321,"text":"That was the great eureka moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125834,"text":"Now, not being able to see meant, of course,"},{"time":128404,"text":"that you taught yourself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129595,"text":"Derek Paravicini: I taught myself to play."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130919,"text":"AO: You did teach yourself to play,"},{"time":132216,"text":"and as a consequence,"},{"time":134747,"text":"playing the piano for you, Derek,"},{"time":135798,"text":"was a lot of knuckles and karate chops,"},{"time":138275,"text":"and even a bit of nose going on in there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140731,"text":"And now, here's what Nanny did also do"},{"time":144059,"text":"was to press the record button on one of those little"},{"time":147381,"text":"early tape recorders that they had,"},{"time":149939,"text":"and this is a wonderful tape, now, of Derek playing"},{"time":152042,"text":"when you were four years old."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153454,"text":"DP: \"Molly Malone (Cockles and Mussels).\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":156152,"text":"AO: It wasn't actually \"Cockles and Mussels.\""},{"time":157214,"text":"This one is \"English Country Garden.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":159364,"text":"DP: \"English Country Garden.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":161629,"text":"(Music: \"English Country Garden\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":198521,"text":"AO: There you are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200319,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207477,"text":"I think that's just fantastic."},{"time":209383,"text":"You know, there's this little child who can't see,"},{"time":211113,"text":"can't really understand much about the world,"},{"time":213320,"text":"has no one in the family who plays an instrument,"},{"time":216026,"text":"and yet he taught himself to play that."},{"time":218327,"text":"And as you can see from the picture,"},{"time":219559,"text":"there was quite a lot of body action going on"},{"time":221918,"text":"while you were playing, Derek."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223719,"text":"Now, along -- Derek and I met when he was four and a half years old,"},{"time":228289,"text":"and at first, Derek, I thought you were mad, to be honest,"},{"time":232107,"text":"because when you played the piano,"},{"time":233921,"text":"you seemed to want to play every single note on the keyboard,"},{"time":236838,"text":"and also you had this little habit"},{"time":238246,"text":"of hitting me out of the way."},{"time":240429,"text":"So as soon as I tried to get near the piano,"},{"time":242235,"text":"I was firmly shoved off."},{"time":244383,"text":"And having said to your dad, Nic,"},{"time":247067,"text":"that I would try to teach you, I was then slightly confused"},{"time":249562,"text":"as to how I might go about that"},{"time":251149,"text":"if I wasn't allowed near the piano."},{"time":253550,"text":"But after a while, I thought, well, the only way"},{"time":255727,"text":"is to just pick you up, shove Derek over to the other side of the room,"},{"time":259828,"text":"and in the 10 seconds that I got before Derek came back,"},{"time":262972,"text":"I could just play something very quickly"},{"time":265149,"text":"for him to learn."},{"time":267141,"text":"And in the end, Derek, I think you agreed"},{"time":268543,"text":"that we could actually have some fun playing the piano together."},{"time":272523,"text":"As you can see, there's me in my early,"},{"time":275348,"text":"pre-marriage days with a brown beard,"},{"time":277587,"text":"and little Derek concentrating there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281233,"text":"I just realized this is going to be recorded, isn't it? Right. Okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283777,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":285079,"text":"Now then, by the age of 10, Derek really"},{"time":289300,"text":"had taken the world by storm."},{"time":291352,"text":"This is a photo of you, Derek, playing at the Barbican"},{"time":294370,"text":"with the Royal Philharmonic Pops."},{"time":296081,"text":"Basically it was just an exciting journey, really."},{"time":300650,"text":"And in those days, Derek, you didn't speak very much,"},{"time":302791,"text":"and so there was always a moment of tension"},{"time":305102,"text":"as to whether you'd actually understood what it was we were going to play"},{"time":308063,"text":"and whether you'd play the right piece in the right key,"},{"time":310574,"text":"and all that kind of thing."},{"time":312033,"text":"But the orchestra were wowed as well,"},{"time":314858,"text":"and the press of the world were fascinated by your ability"},{"time":318715,"text":"to play these fantastic pieces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322052,"text":"Now the question is, how do you do it, Derek?"},{"time":325114,"text":"And hopefully we can show the audience now"},{"time":327685,"text":"how it is you do what you do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330737,"text":"I think that one of the first things that happened"},{"time":332570,"text":"when you were very little, Derek,"},{"time":333847,"text":"was that by the time you were two,"},{"time":336183,"text":"your musical ear had already outstripped that of most adults."},{"time":341162,"text":"And so whenever you heard any note at all --"},{"time":343960,"text":"if I just play a random note --"},{"time":345864,"text":"(Piano notes) --"},{"time":348292,"text":"you knew instantly what it was,"},{"time":350183,"text":"and you'd got the ability as well to find that note on the piano."},{"time":354421,"text":"Now that's called perfect pitch,"},{"time":356009,"text":"and some people have perfect pitch for a few white notes"},{"time":359246,"text":"in the middle of the piano."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360396,"text":"(Piano notes)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":366424,"text":"You can see how -- you get a sense of playing with Derek."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369850,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":373398,"text":"But Derek, your ear is so much more than that."},{"time":376424,"text":"If I just put the microphone down for a bit,"},{"time":377851,"text":"I'm going to play a cluster of notes."},{"time":380571,"text":"Those of you who can see will know how many notes,"},{"time":382887,"text":"but Derek, of course, can't."},{"time":383896,"text":"Not only can you say how many notes,"},{"time":386798,"text":"it's being able to play them all at the same time. Here we are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392222,"text":"(Chords)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":402103,"text":"Well, forget the terminology, Derek. Fantastic."},{"time":404921,"text":"And it's that ability, that ability to hear simultaneous sounds,"},{"time":409866,"text":"not only just single sounds, but when a whole orchestra is playing,"},{"time":412188,"text":"Derek, you can hear every note,"},{"time":414096,"text":"and instantly, through all those hours and hours of practice,"},{"time":417352,"text":"reproduce those on the keyboard,"},{"time":419310,"text":"that makes you, I think, is the basis of all your ability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423577,"text":"Now then."},{"time":426180,"text":"It's no use having that kind of raw ability"},{"time":429748,"text":"without the technique,"},{"time":431509,"text":"and luckily, Derek, you decided that,"},{"time":433431,"text":"once we did start learning, you'd let me help you"},{"time":436053,"text":"learn all the scale fingerings."},{"time":437692,"text":"So for example using your thumb under with C major."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440639,"text":"(Piano notes)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":445752,"text":"Etc."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452161,"text":"And in the end, you got so quick,"},{"time":455521,"text":"that things like \"Flight of the Bumblebee\""},{"time":457395,"text":"were no problem, were they?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":458625,"text":"DP: No."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459903,"text":"AO: Right. So here, by the age of 11,"},{"time":462532,"text":"Derek was playing things like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464504,"text":"DP: This."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467586,"text":"(Music: \"Flight of the Bumblebee\")"},{"time":535792,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537358,"text":"AO: Derek, let's have a bow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551408,"text":"Well done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555480,"text":"Now the truly amazing thing was, with all those scales, Derek,"},{"time":559403,"text":"you could not only play \"Flight of the Bumblebee\""},{"time":561638,"text":"in the usual key, but any note I play,"},{"time":564304,"text":"Derek can play it on."},{"time":566297,"text":"So if I just choose a note at random, like that one."},{"time":568765,"text":"(Piano notes)"},{"time":570580,"text":"Can you play \"Flight of the Bumblebee\" on that note?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":572184,"text":"DP: \"Flight of the Bumblebee\" on that note."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574488,"text":"(Music: \"Flight of the Bumblebee\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":580178,"text":"AO: Or another one? How about in G minor?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":584251,"text":"DP: G minor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586522,"text":"(Music: \"Flight of the Bumblebee\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":591833,"text":"AO: Fantastic. Well done, Derek."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594117,"text":"So you see, in your brain, Derek, is this amazing musical computer"},{"time":597899,"text":"that can instantly recalibrate, recalculate,"},{"time":601598,"text":"all the pieces in the world that are out there."},{"time":603770,"text":"Most pianists would have a heart attack if you said,"},{"time":606197,"text":"\"Sorry, do you mind playing 'Flight of the Bumblebee'"},{"time":608014,"text":"in B minor instead of A minor?\" as we went on."},{"time":611244,"text":"In fact, the first time, Derek, you played that with an orchestra,"},{"time":614665,"text":"you'd learned the version that you'd learned,"},{"time":616754,"text":"and then the orchestra, in fact, did have a different version,"},{"time":618983,"text":"so while we were waiting in the two hours"},{"time":621461,"text":"before the rehearsal and the concert,"},{"time":623463,"text":"Derek listened to the different version and learned it quickly"},{"time":625703,"text":"and then was able to play it with the orchestra."},{"time":628180,"text":"Fantastic chap."}]},{"cues":[{"time":629640,"text":"The other wonderful thing about you is memory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633099,"text":"DP: Memory.\nAO: Your memory is truly amazing, and every concert we do,"},{"time":636935,"text":"we ask the audience to participate, of course,"},{"time":639765,"text":"by suggesting a piece Derek might like to play."},{"time":643529,"text":"And people say, \"Well, that's terribly brave"},{"time":645051,"text":"because what happens if Derek doesn't know it?\""},{"time":647276,"text":"And I say, \"No, it's not brave at all,"},{"time":648288,"text":"because if you ask for something that Derek doesn't know,"},{"time":650940,"text":"you're invited to come and sing it first,"},{"time":652541,"text":"and then he'll pick it up.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":655027,"text":"So just be thoughtful before you suggest something too outlandish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659742,"text":"But seriously, would anyone like to choose a piece?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":663459,"text":"DP: Choose a piece. Choose, choose, would you like to choose?\nAO: Because it's quite dark. You'll just have to shout out."},{"time":667392,"text":"Would you like to hear me play?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":670213,"text":"(Audience: \"Theme of Paganini.\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":671427,"text":"AO: Paganini.\nDP: \"The Theme of Paganini.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":674389,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":676227,"text":"(Music: \"Theme of Paganini\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":771178,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":782409,"text":"AO: Well done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":788223,"text":"Derek's going to L.A. soon,"},{"time":790897,"text":"and it's a milestone, because it means that Derek and I"},{"time":794119,"text":"will have spent over 100 hours on long-haul flights together,"},{"time":797490,"text":"which is quite interesting, isn't it Derek?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":800117,"text":"DP: Very interesting, Adam, yes. Long-haul flights. Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803468,"text":"AO: You may think 13 hours is a long time to keep talking,"},{"time":805930,"text":"but Derek does it effortlessly. Now then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":808448,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":810560,"text":"But in America, they've coined this term,"},{"time":812434,"text":"\"the human iPod\" for Derek,"},{"time":814044,"text":"which I think is just missing the point, really,"},{"time":816400,"text":"because Derek, you're so much more than an iPod."},{"time":819477,"text":"You're a fantastic, creative musician,"},{"time":822264,"text":"and I think that was nowhere clearer to see, really,"},{"time":825215,"text":"than when we went to Slovenia,"},{"time":827412,"text":"and someone -- in a longer concert we tend to get people joining in,"},{"time":832809,"text":"and this person, very, very nervously came onto the stage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":836463,"text":"DP: He played \"Chopsticks.\"\nAO: And played \"Chopsticks.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":838998,"text":"DP: \"Chopsticks.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":840489,"text":"AO: A bit like this.\nDP: Like this. Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":843853,"text":"(Piano notes)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":844791,"text":"AO: I should really get Derek's manager to come and play it."},{"time":846471,"text":"He's sitting there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":847695,"text":"DP: Somebody played \"Chopsticks\" like this.\nAO: Just teasing, right? Here we go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850973,"text":"(Music: \"Chopsticks\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":852229,"text":"DP: Let Derek play it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":854491,"text":"AO: What did you do with it, Derek?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":856064,"text":"DP: I got to improvise with it, Adam."}]},{"cues":[{"time":857805,"text":"AO: This is Derek the musician."},{"time":861372,"text":"(Music: \"Chopsticks\" improvisation)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":917783,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":919860,"text":"(Music) (Clapping)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":923636,"text":"Keep up with Derek."}]},{"cues":[{"time":925777,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":980017,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1003131,"text":"The TED people will kill me,"},{"time":1004579,"text":"but perhaps there's time for one encore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1006635,"text":"DP: For one encore.\nAO: One encore, yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1010460,"text":"So this is one of Derek's heroes."},{"time":1012515,"text":"It's the great Art Tatum --\nDP: Art Tatum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014687,"text":"AO: -- who also was a pianist who couldn't see,"},{"time":1016713,"text":"and also, I think, like Derek,"},{"time":1017870,"text":"thought that all the world was a piano,"},{"time":1019379,"text":"so whenever Art Tatum plays something,"},{"time":1021339,"text":"it sounds like there's three pianos in the room."},{"time":1023974,"text":"And here is Derek's take on Art Tatum's take on \"Tiger Rag.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029798,"text":"DP: \"Tiger Rag.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1033534,"text":"(Music: \"Tiger Rag\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1143869,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}